<div class="text-center text-light">
    
    <h1 class="text-success m-auto p-2 mb-5">Image Processing API Using Sharp</h1>

    <div class="mt-5">
        <h3 class="m-auto p-2 text-white-50">Description</h3>

        <div class="m-auto mt-2 p-4 w-75 border border-danger rounded text-start" style="border-style: dashed !important;">
            <ul><li>Image Cropping/Processing API using Sharp</li></ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-5">
            <h3 class="m-auto p-2 text-white-50">Features</h3>

            <div class="m-auto mt-2 p-4 w-75 border border-danger rounded text-start" style="border-style: dashed !important;">
                    <ol>
                        <li>Crop the image based on the width and height</li>
                        <li>Cashing the requested images</li>
                        <li>Access log for all the requests with unique ID for each entry, The Requestor IP, and Time/Date</li>
                    </ol>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-5">
            <h3 class="m-auto p-2 text-white-50">Instructions</h3>

            <div class="m-auto mt-2 p-4 w-75 border border-danger rounded text-start" style="border-style: dashed !important;">
                <div class="p-2">
                    <h5>To process a new picture:</h5>
                    
                    <ol>
                        <li>Upload your pictures to assets/full</li>
                        <li>Visit http://localhost:3000/api/images?filename=example.jpg&width=100&height=100</li>
                        <li>Replace filename=   with correct picture and provide the extension as .jpg in the parameter</li>
                        <li>Replace width=      with a positive integer bigger than 0</li>
                        <li>Replace height=      with a positive integer bigger than 0</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>

                <div class="p-2">
                    <h5>To display a processed picture:</h5>

                    <ol>
                        <li>Visit http://localhost:3000/api/images?filename=example.jpg&width=100&height=100 with the same parameter as the original request.</li>
                        <li>or Visit http://localhost:3000/api/processed/example-00-00.jpg and replace example...jpg with the processed picture</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>